- Wow! Thanks.

176
00:13:47.369 --> 00:13:48.370
Good luck.

177
00:13:48.453 --> 00:13:51.373
- Hi.
- Steve in the house?

178
00:13:51.456 --> 00:13:52.875
Yes.

179
00:13:53.792 --> 00:13:55.794
- Hey.
- I brought too much wine.

180
00:14:03.260 --> 00:14:04.580
